(2089, 440, 'description', 'Betts Candy Buffets puts a cherry on top of your wedding day with her customised smorgasbord of lollies, desserts and sweet treats. Betts has an inimitable ability for creating a unique and original stunning display.\r\nShe goes above and beyond to compliment your theme and dust you and your\r\nguests in the sweetness of her signature style.\r\nBetts hand makes many of her design and accents and sources only the best\r\nquality products for your decadent pleasure.\r\nBetts offers a tailor made service and specialises in weddings, engagements,\r\nchristenings, birthdays, anniversaries, kids parties, corporate events and much more.\r\n\r\nBetts additionally offers a DIY hire and supply package and has extensive\r\nexperience catering Macedonian Celebrations including Orthodox Ceremony\r\nCandles, pre-wedding celebrations home decor and gift wrapping.\r\nBetts also is able to organise Kids High Tea Pamper Parties associating with\r\nKids Entertainment Sydney that fully style and cater using vintage inspired tea\r\nsets and silverware. Also available upon request, chair and table hire.\r\nLet Betts Candy Buffets provide a little Sweet Treat to make your event\r\ncomplete.'),
