(135, 1, '2015-07-04 06:51:39', '2015-07-04 06:51:39', 'We are your one stop wedding and event planning collective of original artisans who are available to manifest your wildest dreams.\n\nOur vendors are primarily small local businesses with an absolute passion for their profession.\n\nOur services and products are mostly handmade, custom crafted and delivered with love.\n\nWe regularly work together on tailor made events and have a synergy of trust, understanding and creativity.\n\nIn June of 2013 the All Tied Up group was founded over a magical breakfast in Jacie’s garden amid pastel paper flowers, glittering decor, sugar crafted cakes, fresh daisy posies, home baked treats and an awesome side plate of raw and natural talent.\n\nThe original vision was to create a powerful group of service and product providers to refer to and learn from; knowing that they would provide a consistently exceptional outcome for clients and inspire fresh, creative and original ideas.\n\nThe All Tied Up Collective has become a powerful resource for creating a unique, customised and handmade, sentimental experience.\n\nBecause we work and play together we have an intimate understanding of each other and firsthand knowledge of our products and services which makes us a commanding team.\n\nWe put our head, heart and hands into every product and service ensuring you receive a memorable and meaningful, valuable experience.\n\nOur artisans will enthusiastically meet all your wedding and life event planning needs.\n\n&nbsp;', 'Our Vision', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '102-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-07-04 06:51:39', '2015-07-04 06:51:39', '', 102, 'http://localhost/atu/102-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
