(1040, 10, 'description', 'Beautifully created designs printed to add a statement of difference to your special day.\r\n\r\n<em>Jo’s Signs by Design are your one stop shop for hand crafted and computer generated signs, backdrops, indoor banners, labels and specialised print media.</em>\r\n\r\n<em>We strive to create your special event theming vision-all the way from those small, personalised and detailed printed materials, such as place cards, flower girl signs, bridesmaids signs, chocolate bar wrappers, bottle wraps and table plans, to your big picture props, such as candy and dessert buffet backdrops, ice cream parlour shaped signs, free standing Paparazzi walls, A-frame stands and pull up banners for your marketing and promotional materials.</em>\r\n\r\n<em>We offer a complete ‘design through to print’ service or can step in at any point to get whatever job you need done.  </em>\r\n\r\n<em>We have the ability to do single print jobs or bundle multiple items into our custom print packages.</em>\r\n\r\n<em>We work with all imagery and design and are proficient in numerous programs and tools.</em>\r\n\r\n<em>We love to print!!</em>\r\n\r\n<em>“Thank you so much Jo''s Signs By Design your backdrop completed our set up more than 100%.  It was a pleasure dealing with a person like you that gives you all the time that you need.  I will recommend Jo to the world, not just my friends.</em>\r\n\r\n<em>Thank you so much xx”</em>\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Fadi Georgette Awkar</em></strong>\r\n\r\n<em> </em>\r\n\r\n<em>“Special thanks to Jo from Jo''s Signs by Design for the fabulous Pull up Banner she professionally made up for yesterday’s market stall, which also presented our fabulous All Tied Up team at the Run for the Hills Event”</em>\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Melinda Hird Photography</em></strong>\r\n\r\n<em>“Thank you so much for the poster you made for my event. It looked amazing!”</em>\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Ursula Gleis</em></strong>\r\n\r\n<em> </em>\r\n\r\n<em>“Thank you for a wonderful job on Natalie''s banner and bottle labels. They looked fantastic!”</em>\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Regards Carol</em></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Wedding Package;</em></strong><em> save the dates, invitations, maps, wishing well cards, bottle wraps, bonbonniere labels, cake box labels, loot box labels, ceremony signs, guest instruction signs, place cards, table seating plan, welcome Sign, candy buffet backdrop, table runners and thank you notes.</em>\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Bridal Shower Package; </em></strong><em>invitations, candy buffet backdrop, labels, piccolo bottle wraps, chocolate wraps, welcome sign, food labels, thank you notes.</em>\r\n\r\n<em>(this package can be adapted to Kitchen tea)</em>\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Hens/Bucks Night/Week End Package; </em></strong><em>invitations, piccolo/beer bottle wraps, gift bag labels, thank you notes.</em>\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Engagement Party</em></strong><em>; invitations, candy buffet package, thank you notes.</em>\r\n\r\n<em>We have an extensive range of packages or we can custom to your needs.</em>\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Other Events include;</em></strong><em> Milestone Birthdays, Anniversaries, Christenings and Baptisms.  We also have packages for Corporate Events and Functions.</em>'),
